These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, software-developer, social-worker, doctor
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, baccarat, chaman, havana
1. the social-worker is between the chaman-smoker and the baccarat-smoker##2
2. the doctor is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
3. the chaman-smoker is not to the left of the chaman-smoker##8
4. the baccarat-smoker is not the social-worker##6
5. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the accountant##5
6. the accountant is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | doctor  | accountant | social-worker | software-developer  |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | chaman   | havana  | baccarat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, classical, ambient, metal
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, epic, crime
1. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
2. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan of metal##5
3. the fan of gospel is the person watching musical movies##1
4. the fan of metal is between the fan of gospel and the fan of classical##2
5. the fan of classical is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the person watching disaster movies##7
6. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the fan of classical##5
7. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | classical          | metal | gospel     |
| Movie-Genre    | epic      | crime | disaster | musical |

