.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, fanta
4 different pets are kept: rat, snake, lizard, cat
1. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
7. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage           | almond-milk | coffee | cola     | fanta |
| Pet   | snake    | cat   | rat | lizard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, filmmaking, collecting, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, doctor, writer, architect
1. the doctor is on the left of the architect##1
2. the mechanic is not to the left of the doctor##8
3. the writer is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the writer##8
5. the person who's hobby is writing is the mechanic##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the writer##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Hobby   | collecting   | filmmaking         | baking   | writing    |
| Job         | doctor | architect | writer | mechanic |

