.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, country, salsa, r&b
There 4 different types of food: kale, pumpkin, orange, broccoli
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of disco and the fan of country##7
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
3. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the fan of disco##7
4. the fan of salsa is not to the left of the person eating broccoli##8
5. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the fan of country and the person eating pumpkin##7
6. the person eating pumpkin is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5
7. the person eating pumpkin is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | country   | salsa | r&b | disco    |
| Food         | kale | broccoli   | orange   | pumpkin |

