.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
City: nizza, miami, berlin, london
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, whist, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
5. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
6. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person playing domino##8
7. the person traveling to london is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| City          | london | nizza | miami  | berlin |
| Game   | domino   | mah-jongg         | whist | scrabble |

