.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, designer, pilot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror, family, romance
1. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the librarian##8
2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere between the pilot and the person watching family movies##7
3. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
4. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8
5. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the librarian##8
6. the accountant is on the left or right of the designer##3
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
8. the accountant is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Job   | librarian      | designer | accountant | pilot   |
| Movie-Genre      | fantasy | family | romance  | horror |

