.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, fantasy, drama, romance
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, ebony, purple, orange
1. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person who likes brown##2
2. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5
5. the person who likes ebony is the person who likes ebony##1
6. the person watching drama movies is not the person who likes purple##6
7. the person watching romance movies is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
8. the person who likes brown is not to the left of the person who likes ebony##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | horror | drama | fantasy |
| Color     | orange | ebony       | brown  | purple    |

