3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
6. the person who growsbegonia is not to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
