.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, mexican, spanish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, april, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
2. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the argentine##8
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the british##1
4. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3
5. the spanish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the british##7
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the british##3
8. the spanish is on the left or right of the british##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | spanish | british         | mexican    | argentine       |
| Birthday      | december | march | august | april |

