3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
4. the person traveling to miami is between the person traveling to hannover and the owner of the rabbit##2
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| City   | hamburg     | miami | hannover        | prague       |
| Pet      | rabbit | fish  | snake | frog |

