.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, august, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, tennis, ice-hockey, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
4. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
5. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Birthday           | august | november | february | january   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey       | volleyball      | tennis    | skateboarding |

