3. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person traveling to hamburg##2
7. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| City    | hamburg        | liverpool | nizza | miami |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | surfing | climbing   | golf    |

