4. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
5. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
6. the person who growsamaryllis is not to the right of the person who growsaconite##8
7. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who growslily##8

