.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, daffodil, tulip, bellflower
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, orange, pink, mauve
1. the person who likes orange is not the person who growsorchid##6
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is not to the left of the person who likes mauve##8
4. the person who growstulip is the person who likes black##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the person who likes black##7
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
7. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes mauve and the person who growstulip##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Flower         | daffodil    | bellflower | orchid | tulip |
| Color   | orange | mauve      | pink     | black     |

 